            ITA Program office closed until 7/18/2022
          Heading link



 
Copy link



The ITA Program office located in the Student Services Building (SSB) is currently closed to walk-in visitors, and we will be operating remotely until July 18.  Unless otherwise specified, all our testing, courses, and events will be conducted entirely online until that date.
If you have questions regarding ITA testing, courses, or other services, please email us at itap@uic.edu.







